    <h1 style="color: var(--text-color);">Daily Plan: Monday, January 5, 2026 (A.2 Phase 1 Completion + A.3 Scope Planning)</h1>
    
    <div class="alert alert-warning" style="background-color: #fff3cd; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #ff9800; margin: 15px 0;">
        <h3 style="color: #d9534f; margin-top: 0;">⚠️ TIMELINE ADJUSTMENT (Jan 4 Documentation Infrastructure Priority)</h3>
        <p><strong>Note:</strong> Jan 4 focused on establishing daily audit plan infrastructure (variance tracking) rather than A.2 Phase 1. A.2 Phase 1 (Database Connection Pooling) and A.3 Scope Planning are NOW priority for Jan 5-6. Original A.3 audit execution moves to Jan 6+. This ensures proper documentation tracking for all future infrastructure work.</p>
