    <h2>🔴 Priority 1: A.2 K8s Readiness - Phase 1 Completion (2-3 hours) [MOVED FROM JAN 4]</h2>
    
    <p><strong>Complete A.2 Phase 1 - Database Connection Pooling & Specification Finalization:</strong> Incorporate findings from previous analysis and complete the full specification.</p>
    <ol>
        <li><strong>Finalize Database Connection Pooling Design:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Document: Connection limits for multi-pod K8s environment</li>
                <li>Plan: Dynamic connection string via environment variables</li>
                <li>Design: K8s Secrets integration (DB_HOST, DB_USER, DB_PASS, etc.)</li>
                <li>Create: example-secrets.yaml template for K8s deployment</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Complete A.2 Requirements Specification:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>File: /Documentation/A2_Kubernetes_Readiness_Specification.tt</li>
                <li>Add: Implementation checklist (who does what, when)</li>
                <li>Add: Risk assessment and mitigation strategies</li>
                <li>Final review and mark as COMPLETE</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
    </ol>
    <p><strong>Expected Deliverable:</strong> Complete A.2 Requirements Specification (final) + example-secrets.yaml template</p>

    <h2>🟠 Priority 2: A.3 Credentials Audit - Scope & Planning (2-3 hours) [MOVED FROM JAN 4]</h2>
    
    <p><strong>Define A.3 Audit Scope and Create Remediation Plan:</strong> This should have been completed Jan 4 but now moves to Jan 5 to follow A.2 completion.</p>
    <ol>
        <li><strong>Define A.3 Audit Scope:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>List all credential types: API keys, SSH keys, DB passwords, OAuth tokens, TLS certs</li>
                <li>Identify: Where currently stored (code, env vars, secrets manager, .env files)</li>
                <li>Document: Which are likely hardcoded/insecure (plan scope for Jan 6+)</li>
                <li>Plan: Migration timeline to secure secrets management</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Create A.3 Audit Scope Document:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>File: /Documentation/A3_Credentials_Audit_Plan.tt</li>
                <li>Sections: Current State, Scope of Audit, Risk Classification Framework, Remediation Timeline</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
    </ol>
    <p><strong>Expected Deliverable:</strong> A.3 Audit Scope Document + Risk Classification Framework</p>
    
    <h2>🟡 Priority 3: B.1 Docker Secrets - Assessment Phase 1 (1-2 hours)</h2>
    
    <p><strong>Quick assessment to support A.3 scope:</strong> Understand current Docker Secrets usage and what B.1 plan requires.</p>
    <ol>
        <li>Review: Current Docker Compose configurations (secret declarations)</li>
        <li>Identify: What secrets are currently defined vs what's missing</li>
        <li>Plan: B.1 remediation (required for A.3 credentials migration)</li>
    </ol>
    <p><strong>Expected Deliverable:</strong> B.1 Assessment document with remediation plan</p>

